item.title: James H. Conigrave
item.description: I’m a research associate at the Centre for Research Excellence: Indigenous Health and Alcohol. I received a PhD in psychology from ACU. He loves statistics, programming and research automation. I’m interested in the relationship between alcohol consumption and basic psychological need satisfaction.
